          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1631006971956-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has started to caramelise, add your <strong>beluga lentils</strong>, <strong>chopped potato</strong>,<strong> diced carrot </strong>and <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
