    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> tomato paste</strong> and<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[350ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
