    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 15 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender – this is your <strong>lentil</strong> <strong>curry pie filling</strong></p><p>Whilst everything’s cooking, wash then rip the leaves off your <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 6,
